MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Adds the flesh layer that makes differentiated cells actually think. Given a seed
spec (question + role-assigned agents + grounding evidence), LearningCycle runs:
  researchers produce grounded findings
  -> critics adversarially score each finding
  -> a finding's stored confidence is the MEAN critic score (earned, not self-rated)
  -> synthesizer composes reviewed findings into a candidate artifact
  -> all emitted as KnowledgeRecordV0 (the OAA -> AAA boundary file)

CognitionProvider is the shell contract; AnthropicCognition (Claude) and
DeterministicCognition (offline fallback) are swappable flesh. Output is grounded
only in caller-supplied evidence — agents do not invent sources.

CLI: python -m src.cognition.run_cycle --seed seed.json --out artifacts.jsonl

Validated live with Agentic-AI-Architect: a 3-researcher/2-critic/1-synthesizer
cycle produced artifacts scored 0.64-0.72 by adversarial critics; AAA promoted the
one clearing its 0.70 gate and measured the answer relevance rise 0.669 -> 0.777.

